Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hello
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到你居然會敗給那種小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是對你滿懷期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你還是靠自己想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙死了忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「暴走」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾先生也好你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君有許多可怕的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是那傢伙的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅家和日向家的人根本不可能有所謂的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是支配者 而我們只能遵從
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不可能萌生出所謂的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君是不會這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是自由自在長大成人的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他不再是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}了 立場卻從未改變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換句話就是從容不迫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他真的把我當成朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是年少時的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話就說到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會認識匡平也算是你不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨的話就恨那傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久羽子?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是金屬制的球杆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會出現在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我調查了一下空守村的事情之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 總之發生了許多事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你這副模樣還真引人遐想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人氣很高的日日乃這幅模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是拍下來的話一定可以賣個好價錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道了 快幫我解開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到會在這種地方回歸到我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然會找到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然綁架女人 你在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃 去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 久羽子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久羽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久羽子 久羽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久羽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我大意了 空張久羽子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 快開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身為議員做這種事情會很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂 反正我多的是替死鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久羽子 你太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很擔心你哦 不如放她進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再磨蹭了 趕緊逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把這裡打開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了我一個人身手敏捷逃起來更加容易嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了你快點逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你居然會為了朋友而擔心至此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人不禁落淚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是說了實話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要對付你 只靠我一個人便綽綽有餘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久羽子 久羽子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 我立刻去叫人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平大人他不願意和我一起回村子裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是被甩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼認為 史場日日乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在得救久羽子...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有槍...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空張 你這混蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕緊逃走吧 老公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 在員警來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是匡平大人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼問 無論如何我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是非常從容嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是覺得自己贏過了我才擺出那副態度的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼匡平大人憎恨著村子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(730,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要放棄身為{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}的立場?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(785,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且還放棄了{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明是如此強大和帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠以其力量降服所有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們按照自己的意志來行動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君他...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君他曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過強的力量會給人帶來不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.86,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(930,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說他明明擁有著如此強大的{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.22,0:09:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻還有不能得到手的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是指是否能夠得到手的問題...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果什麼都能得到手的話又怎麼會陷入不幸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼匡平大人要說那樣的話?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.58,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}的力量是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:33.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(130,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}是我能在那個村子 那個家裡生存下去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然說這是錯誤的力量?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋 別突然飛出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我們下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君 你是怎麼知道這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空張打電話告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了 久羽子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她讓我一個人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽見了槍聲 在那之後...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再做丟臉的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將妨礙我的傢伙統統打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後得到匡平大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝妹妹 快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(830,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝 我已經不再是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你依舊可以和我一起回到村子裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和你一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:10:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝姐姐沒有收手的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我擁有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我來教會你們人與人的優劣之分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也有著戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你踩碎了我的小餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我道歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是在這麼寬廣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.43,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃{\r}是無法張開結界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好當做是對你的讓步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你制伏的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太小看了我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼戰鬥方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被它拽下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君 快阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能讓他們一直打到消氣為止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真晝姐姐和詩緒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想好不容易找到他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然已經先給我大鬧起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣也根本阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰...誰會去關心詩緒她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝 你變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起 真虧你能...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還嫩得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的匡平大人他...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不要扭打在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.54,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在{\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃{\r}的結界缺少了一條觸角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此張開結界需要花費一定的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一瞬間的可乘之機就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊  詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼呆啊 想殺了我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站起來 {\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的話啊 {\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我飛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(730,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來 {\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝姐姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她所期望的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:25.31,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\pos(40,650)\c&H1414FF&}マガツヒ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\c&H1414FF&}禍津妃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}沒用的 真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}支配系統完全被切斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}所以你的命令...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝妹妹還是快住手吧
